{"id":"6947","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【精灵研究所】“矩阵”精灵周刊 Vol.2 雷电猴","content":"<p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">大家好，我是科普喵。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;各位训练师都应该听说过，在源码学园里，有这么一座矗立在科学研究高峰的顶端的研究所，但是很少有人能进入其中。没错，那就是以达尔文博士为领军人物的矩阵研究中心。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;根据达尔文博士的指示，为了向各位训练师带来最新鲜的精灵研究资讯，以及最超前的精灵信息公开，矩阵研究所特意与源码时代杂志社合作推出了‘矩阵’精灵周刊。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">科普解谜题，精灵零距离。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">那么快来看看本周的精灵周刊都有哪些内容吧！</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>※ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ※</u></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\">&nbsp;精灵头条&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgKX5RSBoPAiVvqym091iSvXJLj1\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\"><br></font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;010.雷电猴&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">属性：电&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">星级：三星&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">喜欢的食物：电池/香蕉&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">最大的梦想：能够储备发电站级别的电量。&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">雷电猴是一种黄色的小型精灵，身上有着代表电流的黑色绝缘皮肤，头上有着类似避雷针的触角。它的手上有着能够放电的爪子，会以快速旋转手臂的方式来加速发出电流。源码世界出现的偶然停电大多时候都是因为大量雷电猴聚集在一起吞食电力而造成的，暴风雨来时雷电猴会偷偷爬到树上等闪电会落下的高处，以吸引落雷。&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>※ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ※</u></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\">精灵小常识</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;1</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">电气袋。面颊的红色部分藏有电力袋，揉搓电力袋之后便会放射出大量电流。&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;2</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">电力过载。一旦雷电猴积蓄了大量的电力时，脾气偶尔会失控而变得暴躁，直到过载的电量被释放之后才恢复。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">3</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">电火花效应。当身体里储存满电时，头上的触角之间会剧烈地迸发出炫目的蓝白色火花。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">电荷释放。当电力过多的时候，雷电猴就把双手插在地上以释放电力，有时候会烧焦附近的植被。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">5</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">共享电源。当多只雷电猴在一起时，电量较多的雷电猴会以连接手臂的方式来交换电流给较少的雷电猴，以保持彼此电量处于稳定值。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>※ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ※</u></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\">精灵特殊技能&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">1&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">电磁炮&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">利用强大的逆电磁效应，把身体里储备的全部电流汇集起来喷向对方。 研究所报告：电磁炮的破坏力极强，以致于雷电猴使用之后会有很长一段时间动弹不得。研究所依然在研究如何使电流转化成冲击力这么强的形式。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;2&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">静电&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">辅助能力&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">当敌人直接接触到雷电猴的身体时有几率被麻痹。 研究所报告：除了雷电猴身上黑色的绝缘区以外，都有着静电的存在。&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>※ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ※</u></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\">相关评价</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;“啊啊啊我爱雷电猴！！！！！！” --阿正 “</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">当你遇到雷电猴的时候，问好就可以了，千万不要尝试和它握手，别问我是怎么知道的！” --阿短</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>※ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ※</u></p>\n<p></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\">猜猜我是谁？</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqO8_-FxC5Nf7XBIVY5ARrLqA5Cm\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p></p>","board_id":"7","board_name":"灌水池塘","updated_at":1507872130,"created_at":1507802074,"n_views":114,"n_replies":7,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":true,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}